Private Derivatives() As Double
Private Bias() As Double
Private BiasDelta() As Double
Private BiasMean() As Double
Private BiasVar() As Double
Private WeightDeltas() As Double
Private DeltaMean() As Double
Private DeltaVar() As Double
Private ActivationFunctions() As Integer
Private NeuronCounts() As Long
Private LearningRate As Double
Private ReLUConst As Double
